name: Ashley Tervort
description:
Ashley Tervort, a popular OnlyFans model a couple of years ago, was notable for her big "eyes". Now retired or something.

To train the model, I chose a photo from her prime year, when she gained maximum weight.

Make sure you dress her up well before generating pictures, like all OnlyFans girls, she loves to show off her charms.

I hope someone likes this TI. I'm still just learning and practicing, so please don't judge me too hard)

I recommend reduced weight. For example, "(ashterv:0.95)" works fine in most cases for version 2

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Completely created a new TI from scratch. I chose other photos, made other settings. Ashley lost some weight but gained in quality)

I recommend reduced weight. For example, "(ashterv:0.95)" works fine in most cases
